page_0: "Personal Notes

Tested Marten's suggested settings on prototype today:

Efficiency of solar reception went slightly down while lunar reception improved at astonishing rate. Keeping spectral receptor active also during nighttime seems reasonable; going to recommend adjustments to Director Wilkerson.

Must locate Marten and ask how he calculated these figures. He claimed to have come all the way from the City just to visit me, and he even knew I had based the receptor on Precursor technology. Evidently, my reputation precedes me."